oster represents the country's faith that he has overcome the serious injuries from his crash in 2022 that have plagued hisperformanceuntil this year.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombian_National_Time_Trial_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colombian time trial\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombian_National_Time_Trial_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombian_National_Time_Trial_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egan_Bernal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2637905868504195e-35, \"text\": \"Bernal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egan_Bernal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egan_Bernal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bernal is currently third overall at the Tour de Suisse and finishedthird overall in the Volta a Catalunyaand O Gran Cami\\u00f1o earlier this season.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Suisse\", \"score\": 0.9962630812049196, \"rank\": 0.0037509357363094266, \"text\": \"Tour de Suisse\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Suisse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Suisse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also has a limited history of performances in one-day races, taking third in Il Lombardia in 2019 behind compatriot Esteban Chaves.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_di_Lombardia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3974795540518305e-24, \"text\": \"Il Lombardia\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_di_Lombardia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d